reviews.review_text: Thank you! Thanks to Tony or Mike or whoever uploaded this and the 3/31/84 show. I've always loved these shows (especially the 2nd sets) and finally can listen to them as they ought to be heard. The Slipknot is spliced up weird on the SBD version and I lost my only copy of the AUD of this show that I had on tape. These are such incredible shows and these AUD versions are great. Can't wait to crank them up!!!

stunning aud tape wow, the depth and frequency response of this tape is amazing!

put on some good cans and give set II a listen.  AM Dew will give you goosebumps!
